description._content: Description: Palestine Roads - Road Bridge over R.Jordan where it flows out of Sea of Galilee, near Semakh. Location: Palestine Date: 1922 Description: Palestine Roads - Road Bridge over R.Jordan, North Dead Sea. (Goraniyeh Bridge). Location: Palestine Date: 1922 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/733 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
